sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant FileSystem
    participant Editor

    User->>App: Click "Open File"
    App->>FileSystem: Open dialog
    FileSystem-->>User: Select file
    User->>App: Confirm selection
    App->>FileSystem: Read file content
    FileSystem-->>App: Return content
    App->>Editor: Load content
    Editor-->>User: Display editor + preview

    alt Markdown file
        Editor->>Editor: Render with TipTap
    else Mermaid file
        Editor->>Editor: Render with Mermaid
    end

    User->>Editor: Edit content
    Editor->>FileSystem: Auto-save (debounced)
    FileSystem-->>Editor: Save confirmed
